headline: Does Realty Income's (O) European Expansion and Equity Offering Shift the Long-Term Risk Profile?
summary: On November 7, 2025, Realty Income Corporation declared its 665th consecutive monthly dividend and announced a follow-on equity offering of 150,000,000 shares through an at-the-market program, payable to shareholders of record as of November 28, 2025.
